2001-01-28  Steve Robbins  <steve@nyongwa.montreal.qc.ca>

	* configure.in: Filter $MNI_LIBS to replace -lfoo by the path to
	"libfoo.la", if it exists.  Set up for libtool using AM_PROG_LIBTOOL.
	This allows libtool to link correctly against "libbicpl".

2001-01-26  Steve ROBBINS  <stever@bic.mni.mcgill.ca>

	* callbacks/Makefile.am (INCLUDES): Include $(malloc_CFLAGS).

	* callbacks/call_globals.c (DEF_MENU_FUNCTION): Make code
	conditional on HAVE_MALLINFO symbol, rather than !linux && !__sun.

	* configure.in: Checkfor mallinfo() in -lmalloc; define
	HAVE_MALLINFO, if found.

	* Makefile.am (Display.menu): Use $(top_srcdir) to find
	input file.
	(Display_LDADD): Link with Xmu, and $(malloc_LIBS).

